      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "これは、数学のテストか？\n点数は……100点じゃないか！",
      "startTime": 7.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.8941949368
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　テストで満点を取れたんです！\n沙季ちゃんに勉強を教えてもらった甲斐がありました！",
      "startTime": 14.1270747185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "よく頑張ったな。でも、これ……\nよく見ると学校のテストじゃないような……",
      "startTime": 20.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.511927398
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "実はそれ、沙季ちゃんが作ったテストなんです",
      "startTime": 24.511927398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "寮で一週間、毎日勉強会を開いて\n最終日に沙季ちゃんが作ったテストを受けたんです",
      "startTime": 32.0476642926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.8118815899
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "そうしたら本当に100点を取れて\nびっくりしちゃいました",
      "startTime": 38.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.4785481135
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "沙季の教え方がうまいのもあるかもしれないが\n何より、さくらが真面目に頑張った成果だな",
      "startTime": 43.8034074157,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "沙季ちゃんも「よく頑張りましたね」って\n私の頭を撫でて褒めてくれました",
      "startTime": 50.1678229014,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.7054634729
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "勉強会で一緒に教わっていた千紗ちゃん、琴乃ちゃん\n渚ちゃんも同じテストを受けたんですけど……",
      "startTime": 58.0011562347,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.6845554034
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "千紗ちゃんと渚ちゃんも100点だったんですよ！\n凄いと思いませんか？",
      "startTime": 65.1344888051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それは凄い……一人足りなくないか？",
      "startTime": 67.4642152786,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.2061651866
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "あ……琴乃ちゃんは、沙季ちゃんの補習を\n受けることになっちゃいました……",
      "startTime": 76.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "しかし、本当に100点を取るなんて……\nこの調子で他のリストも達成出来るといいな",
      "startTime": 83.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.6295664151
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "他のリストと言えば、聞いて下さい！\n昨日、kanaさんが英会話を教えてくれたんです",
      "startTime": 89.7893866856,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.1132205328
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "見かける度に駆け寄って声を掛けて、教えてほしいって\n何度もお願いして、やっと引き受けてくれたんですよ",
      "startTime": 97.8817618266,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "kanaさんもさくらには根負けしたか……",
      "startTime": 102.455578518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.4905898572
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "簡単な日常会話を教えてもらって\nその場でkanaさんと英語で話したんです",
      "startTime": 108.3897032253,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.2775737286
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "私の英語を「はいはい上手上手」って褒めてくれて……\nこれでリストにあった「英会話をする」、達成です！",
      "startTime": 116.6075076103,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "本気で褒めているかは微妙だが……\n達成出来て良かったな",
      "startTime": 124.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.4767345429
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "それから、週末には遙子ちゃんと山に登って\n「ヤッホーと叫ぶ」をやる予定なんです",
      "startTime": 130.2418840726,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "凄い勢いでリストを消化しているな。この調子なら\nやりたいことを全部達成してしまうんじゃないか？",
      "startTime": 138.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 142.0487300556
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02-skr015.m4a",
      "text": "全部はさすがに無理ですよ。リストはまだまだ\n残ってますし、中には実現不可能なものもありますから",
      "startTime": 146.0449908257,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 151.2487112047
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02-skr016.m4a",
      "text": "「さくらちゃんと一緒に流星群を見る」とか「さくら\nちゃんと一緒に麻奈ちゃんのライブを観る」とか……",
      "startTime": 155.6914551817,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 160.0921805701
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02-skr017.m4a",
      "text": "出来るなら私も叶えたいけど……\n友ちゃんはもういないから、さすがに無理ですよね",
      "startTime": 164.0783277195,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 168.1759444874
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "それは、考え方によるんじゃないか？　俺もたまに\n「この光景を麻奈に見せたかった」と思うことがあるが",
      "startTime": 172.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そういう時、俺は麻奈が近くにいるように感じるんだ\nきっとそばで見てくれているって……",
      "startTime": 180.9999949138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 183.7850090345
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "大切な人を想う時、その人はそばにいる……\nそう思うのは都合が良過ぎるかな？",
      "startTime": 188.7999949138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 191.7248732249
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_13_02-skr018.m4a",
      "text": "……いえ、素敵な考え方だと思います",
      "startTime": 192.309904162,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
